OL,3,CThousands of pupils receive their exam
OL,4,Cresults
OL,6,FThousands of pupils across southern
OL,7,FScotland have received their National,
OL,8,FHigher and Advanced Higher exam
OL,9,Fresults today.
OL,11,FStudents from the Scottish Borders sat
OL,12,Fmore than 13,500 examinations this
OL,13,Fyear, achieving the highest grade
OL,14,Fpercentages across the last five years.
OL,16,FExam statistics in the Scottish
OL,17,FBorders:
OL,19,F- 97% of S4 students achieved a
OL,20,Fliteracy award
