OL,3,CThousands of pupils receive their exam
OL,4,Cresults
OL,6,F- 96% of S4 pupils achieved a National
OL,7,FEnglish award
OL,9,F- 90% of S4 students achieved a
OL,10,Fnumeracy award
OL,12,F- 84% of S4 pupils achieved a National
OL,13,F5 Maths award
OL,15,FAttending the exam results day at
OL,16,FPeebles High School, Cllr Julie Pirone
OL,17,Fsaid the results demonstrate the
OL,18,F"remarkable resilience and continued
OL,19,Fdedication" of young people across the
OL,20,FScottish Borders.
