OL,6,FShe added: "It is important to
OL,7,Fremember that every pupil is different
OL,8,Fand will have their own ambition. For
OL,9,Fsome, these results will be vital in
OL,10,Fgetting a place at university, and for
OL,11,Fothers they will be an important step
OL,12,Ftowards a job, a Modern
OL,13,FApprenticeship, further education or
OL,14,Fcontinuing their next school year.
OL,16,F"Our secondary schools work extremely
OL,17,Fhard with the SQA and many other
OL,18,Fpartners throughout the year and are
OL,19,Fcommitted to ensuring that every young
OL,20,Fperson can fulfil their potential.
