OL,3,CThousands of pupils receive their exam
OL,4,Cresults
OL,6,F"It is therefore encouraging to see
OL,7,Fthat our commitment to preparing our
OL,8,Fyoung people for their next steps in
OL,9,Flife continues to pay dividends, with
OL,10,Fan increasing number of them being
OL,11,Fable to leave education with higher
OL,12,Flevels of qualifications and
OL,13,Fattainment and move on to positive and
OL,14,Fsustained destinations.
OL,16,F"It is important to remember that
OL,17,Fthere is no wrong path, and what's
OL,18,Fimportant is that we help young people
OL,19,Fto arrive at a positive destination."
